<span class='tline' id='l7' data-llen='155:181'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0090', 'WYG', '006-1a' );" name="006-1a" class="pb">[006-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l8' data-llen='181:189'>欽定四庫全書</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='189:210'>　泰泉鄉禮卷六　　　　　　明　黄佐　撰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='210:216'>　　保甲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='216:239'>　凡一社之内一家為一牌十牌為一甲甲有總十甲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='239:262'>　　為一保保有長為保長者専一倡率甲總防禦盜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='262:285'>　　賊不許因而武斷鄉曲推選才行為衆所信服者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='285:308'>　　充之或即以約正帶管　保甲本明道程子為晉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='308:331'>　　城令時保伍法也其法量鄉里逺近為保伍使之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='331:357'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0090', 'WYG', '006-1b' );" name="006-1b" class="pb">[006-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='357:380'>　　力役相助患難相卹奸偽無所容孤㷀老疾者責</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='380:403'>　　親黨使無失所行旅出扵其途者疾病皆有所養</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='403:426'>　　及王安石行保甲法則督民操練使自備衣甲器</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='426:449'>　　械天下始騷然矣故今以鄉約為主有可推選者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='449:472'>　　立為保長如無其人即以約正為之長聫乎總總</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='472:495'>　　聫乎牌牌聫乎家大小相維善惡相核一社之内</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='495:518'>　　惡少自無所容一遇盜警保長統率各甲防截追</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='518:541'>　　捕其設置之費除粉牌所用者不多令一牌内十</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='541:567'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0090', 'WYG', '006-2a' );" name="006-2a" class="pb">[006-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='567:590'>　　家攢置外其扵鄉社前量行起立望臺土基亦令</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='590:613'>　　社夫自築或起更樓一座則量行葢造買辦鑼鼔</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='613:636'>　　及造册紙張之類俱約正約副與富家自備俱不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='636:659'>　　許科擾扵民立法大要在扵保安良善消弭盜賊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='659:682'>　　而已中間有愚昧妄自驚疑及隣鄉彼此平素不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='682:705'>　　和者鄉先生及教讀等務委曲開諭之仍各給告</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='705:712'>　　示通知</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='712:732'>　凡立牌有三一曰戒諭二曰沿門三曰十家</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='732:758'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0090', 'WYG', '006-2b' );" name="006-2b" class="pb">[006-2b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l35' data-llen='758:767'>　戒諭者置于社</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l36' data-llen='767:790'>　一欽奉太祖髙皇帝戒諭立牌一面長一尺二寸廣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l37' data-llen='790:813'>　　如之大書六語于上置于鄉社或鄉校行鄉約則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l38' data-llen='813:835'>　　社祝讀之不必家至户到皆立此牌徒為文具</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l39' data-llen='835:842'>　戒諭牌式</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l40' data-llen='842:861'>　　　　　欽　　孝順父母　尊敬長上</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l41' data-llen='861:880'>　　　　　奉　　和睦鄉里　教訓子孫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l42' data-llen='880:899'>　　　　　戒　　各安生理　莫作非為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l43' data-llen='899:925'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0090', 'WYG', '006-3a' );" name="006-3a" class="pb">[006-3a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l44' data-llen='925:933'>　　　　　諭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l45' data-llen='933:942'>　沿門者登于冊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l46' data-llen='942:965'>　一各家俱用方尺紙牌照式明白書冩置門楣上以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l47' data-llen='965:988'>　　便鄉老查考約正約副公同保長人等造冊次第</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l48' data-llen='988:1011'>　　書之一様三本約正鄉老保長各執其一如約正</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l49' data-llen='1011:1034'>　　即為保長則一様二本毎家之後量留半頁以備</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l50' data-llen='1034:1042'>　　陸續開報</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l51' data-llen='1042:1051'>　各家門面牌式</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l52' data-llen='1051:1077'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0090', 'WYG', '006-3b' );" name="006-3b" class="pb">[006-3b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l53' data-llen='1077:1101'>　　某府州縣某處某鄉社<span class='krp-note'>如寺觀庵/院亦倣此</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l54' data-llen='1101:1141'>　　　一户某人<span class='krp-note'>係某衛所某官下舎餘或某總小旗/甲下軍餘或某坊都某坊廂里長某</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l55' data-llen='1141:1167'>　　　　　　　<span class='krp-note'>下軍民匠竈等籍/若係僧道亦倣此</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l56' data-llen='1167:1195'>　　　　男子㡬丁　某人<span class='krp-note'>係官/吏</span>某人<span class='krp-note'>作何/生理</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l57' data-llen='1195:1229'>　　　　　某人<span class='krp-note'>在某處/買賣</span>某人<span class='krp-note'>係生/員</span>某人<span class='krp-note'>有何/手藝</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l58' data-llen='1229:1256'>　　　　　某人<span class='krp-note'>見當/某役</span>　某人<span class='krp-note'>有何殘/廢疾</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l59' data-llen='1256:1273'>　　　　婦女㡬口<span class='krp-note'>無則/不開</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l60' data-llen='1273:1288'>　　一田若干畆該糧若干石斗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l61' data-llen='1288:1314'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0090', 'WYG', '006-4a' );" name="006-4a" class="pb">[006-4a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l62' data-llen='1314:1340'>　　一房屋門面幾間<span class='krp-note'>或自已置買或/典賃某人屋住</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l63' data-llen='1340:1379'>　　一寄住客某人<span class='krp-note'>係某府州縣人某年月日来家典/住或寄歇作何生理或在某衙門</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l64' data-llen='1379:1405'>　　　　　　　　<span class='krp-note'>幹某勾當或為人/傭工陸續開報</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l65' data-llen='1405:1414'>　　一牛若干頭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l66' data-llen='1414:1434'>　　一馬若干匹<span class='krp-note'>已上三條/無則不開</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l67' data-llen='1434:1457'>　　　右件除城内居人士夫羣聚禮義素明宜自有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l68' data-llen='1457:1480'>　　　處不必編牌或都會繁華人烟輳雜則酌而行</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l69' data-llen='1480:1503'>　　　之城外不問闗廂鎮店不問軍衛有司不問庵</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l70' data-llen='1503:1529'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0090', 'WYG', '006-4b' );" name="006-4b" class="pb">[006-4b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l71' data-llen='1529:1552'>　　　堂寺觀不問深山窮谷通行開報冊除十嵗以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l72' data-llen='1552:1575'>　　　下小兒不報十嵗以上者俱上牌冊凡五丁出</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l73' data-llen='1575:1598'>　　　一丁上十家牌輪當甲總葢取四人營運以治</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l74' data-llen='1598:1621'>　　　内一人守望以治外之意也大家則析如有人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l75' data-llen='1621:1644'>　　　十丁則取二丁上牌有二十丁則取四丁上牌</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l76' data-llen='1644:1667'>　　　五十丁則取五丁上牌小家則併如止有人三</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l77' data-llen='1667:1690'>　　　四丁不足五丁者則相併之務足五丁之數保</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l78' data-llen='1690:1713'>　　　長約正約副教讀鄉老社祝之家俱免輪當甲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l79' data-llen='1713:1739'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0090', 'WYG', '006-5a' );" name="006-5a" class="pb">[006-5a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l80' data-llen='1739:1762'>　　　總其寺觀庵院或㳺僧抄化或住持道衆俱要</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l81' data-llen='1762:1785'>　　　明開下落若在荒野園圃住居者則開係某人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l82' data-llen='1785:1808'>　　　産業一體上冊若冊内無名即係鄉約不取保</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l83' data-llen='1808:1831'>　　　甲不容自外于王化者也衛屯營或獨設一地</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l84' data-llen='1831:1854'>　　　或與民相攙俱不得紛更軍民一體編告正軍</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l85' data-llen='1854:1877'>　　　并城操及跟某官常川役占者俱明白開除免</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l86' data-llen='1877:1900'>　　　上十家牌輪當甲總與社相近者即附入社内</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l87' data-llen='1900:1923'>　　　其各州縣及軍屯原設地方火甲營長等項俱</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l88' data-llen='1923:1949'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0090', 'WYG', '006-5b' );" name="006-5b" class="pb">[006-5b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l89' data-llen='1949:1972'>　　　仍舊以應承接逓及官府公事差遣其新編保</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l90' data-llen='1972:1995'>　　　長之屬各鄉以聞于在城四大館轉達有司優</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l91' data-llen='1995:2007'>　　　免身役毋致勞擾</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l92' data-llen='2007:2015'>十家者輪于甲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l93' data-llen='2015:2038'>　一各家沿門開報小牌約正約副公同教讀編造成</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l94' data-llen='2038:2061'>　　冊乃以十家為一甲共為一大牌每五丁抽一丁</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l95' data-llen='2061:2084'>　　精壯者上牌輪當甲總十甲則為一保皆保長統</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l96' data-llen='2084:2107'>　　領之各甲不立甲頭者所以防脅制侵擾之弊也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l97' data-llen='2107:2133'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0090', 'WYG', '006-6a' );" name="006-6a" class="pb">[006-6a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l98' data-llen='2133:2150'>　　惟使之日相輪當甲總則無弊矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l99' data-llen='2150:2157'>十家牌面式</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l100' data-llen='2157:2169'>　某縣某坊鄉圖第㡬甲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l101' data-llen='2169:2179'>　　　上甲尾某人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l102' data-llen='2179:2201'>　　　本甲一户某人　男子幾丁某人輪當甲總</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l103' data-llen='2201:2223'>　　　本甲一户某人　男子幾丁某人輪當甲總</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l104' data-llen='2223:2245'>　　　本甲一户某人　男子幾丁某人輪當甲總</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l105' data-llen='2245:2267'>　　　本甲一户某人　男子幾丁某人輪當甲總</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l106' data-llen='2267:2293'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0090', 'WYG', '006-6b' );" name="006-6b" class="pb">[006-6b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l107' data-llen='2293:2315'>　　　本甲一户某人　男子幾丁某人輪當甲總</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l108' data-llen='2315:2337'>　　　本甲一户某人　男子幾丁某人輪當甲總</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l109' data-llen='2337:2359'>　　　本甲一户某人　男子幾丁某人輪當甲總</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l110' data-llen='2359:2381'>　　　本甲一户某人　男子幾丁某人輪當甲總</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l111' data-llen='2381:2403'>　　　本甲一户某人　男子幾丁某人輪當甲總</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l112' data-llen='2403:2425'>　　　本甲一户某人　男子幾丁某人輪當甲總</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l113' data-llen='2425:2435'>　　　下甲頭某人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l114' data-llen='2435:2458'>　　　右件十家共置一大牌照式開冩日輪一家當</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l115' data-llen='2458:2484'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0090', 'WYG', '006-7a' );" name="006-7a" class="pb">[006-7a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l116' data-llen='2484:2507'>　　　甲總沿門曉諭因而審察各家動靜但有面目</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l117' data-llen='2507:2530'>　　　生疎之人蹤跡可疑之事及違條約不聴勸諭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l118' data-llen='2530:2550'>　　　者即行報官究治或有隠匿十家連罪</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l119' data-llen='2550:2566'>乃以八事糾察在社之民而勸懲之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l120' data-llen='2566:2589'>　一曰遵戒諭　甲内俱要父慈子孝兄友弟恭夫和</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l121' data-llen='2589:2612'>　　婦順善相勸勉惡相規戒患難相恤出入相友小</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l122' data-llen='2612:2635'>　　心以奉官法勤謹以辦國課皆仰遵聖製戒諭之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l123' data-llen='2635:2658'>　　意也但有不遵條約者務要互相勸導果不聴改</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l124' data-llen='2658:2684'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0090', 'WYG', '006-7b' );" name="006-7b" class="pb">[006-7b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l125' data-llen='2684:2706'>　　稟官罰治凡有水火盜賊俱要齊心併力救䕶</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l126' data-llen='2706:2729'>　二曰慎宥罰　甲内但有平日習為奸盜及窩通賊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l127' data-llen='2729:2752'>　　黨容寄賊贓者同甲俱要首報在官許其改過自</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l128' data-llen='2752:2775'>　　新凡遇警竊即於此輩中挨查但有隠匿甲内坐</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l129' data-llen='2775:2798'>　　以知情重罪若有睹博無藉教唆健訟造言生事</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l130' data-llen='2798:2821'>　　詐稱名目恃強凌弱受人投獻或燒香聚衆習為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l131' data-llen='2821:2844'>　　鬼教與私通外國透漏邊情而同甲不行勸阻及</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l132' data-llen='2844:2867'>　　勸阻不聴而不稟告官司者悉重加罰治其稔惡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l133' data-llen='2867:2893'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0090', 'WYG', '006-8a' );" name="006-8a" class="pb">[006-8a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l134' data-llen='2893:2916'>　　不改者即便捕送官司明正典刑違者約正約副</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l135' data-llen='2916:2926'>　　保長一體連坐</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l136' data-llen='2926:2949'>　三曰聨守望　甲内各家輪當甲總者俱要備器械</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l137' data-llen='2949:2972'>　　置鑼鼓但有盜警一家擊鼓各家相連齊擊一巷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l138' data-llen='2972:2995'>　　擊鼓各巷相連齊擊但聞警鼓各家男婦大小俱</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l139' data-llen='2995:3018'>　　執器械出於門首排立其丁壯上十家牌者遇有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l140' data-llen='3018:3041'>　　奔賊即要齊出併力截捕但有後期不赴者同甲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l141' data-llen='3041:3064'>　　舉告官司量加罰治其社前鑼鼓及懸於更樓者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l142' data-llen='3064:3090'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0090', 'WYG', '006-8b' );" name="006-8b" class="pb">[006-8b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l143' data-llen='3090:3113'>　　聞盜發亂擊之旁村鄉社始聞者以一擊為莭次</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l144' data-llen='3113:3136'>　　二次三俄頃之間聲布百里皆發丁壯上十家牌</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l145' data-llen='3136:3159'>　　者嚴守險要故守望相連而盜賊無可逃也其或</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l146' data-llen='3159:3182'>　　藩籬太分爾汝太别東隣被盜而西隣閉户南村</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l147' data-llen='3182:3205'>　　殺人而北村袖手此家失盜而彼家接買此鄉捕</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l148' data-llen='3205:3228'>　　捉而彼鄉窩隠者事宜宻報四隅大館以憑稟官</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l149' data-llen='3228:3234'>　　懲治</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l150' data-llen='3234:3257'>　四曰時操練　甲内遇有盜警保長約正人等㸃閘</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l151' data-llen='3257:3283'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0090', 'WYG', '006-9a' );" name="006-9a" class="pb">[006-9a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l152' data-llen='3283:3306'>　　壯丁上十家牌者各執戈㦸聴閱練鳴鑼擊鼓以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l153' data-llen='3306:3329'>　　操習之操必於早晨操已歸服舊業其不聴操練</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l154' data-llen='3329:3336'>　　者必罰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l155' data-llen='3336:3359'>　五曰嚴約束　保内大小人家凡有故而出者須赴</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l156' data-llen='3359:3382'>　　約正保長處報知返則告銷俱不得輕自出入敢</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l157' data-llen='3382:3405'>　　有不告而出及朝在而夕遯者約正人等根究來</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l158' data-llen='3405:3418'>　　歴果涉違法送官懲治</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l159' data-llen='3418:3441'>　六曰稽去住　保内已經編造甲之後或有寄住客</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l160' data-llen='3441:3467'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0090', 'WYG', '006-9b' );" name="006-9b" class="pb">[006-9b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l161' data-llen='3467:3490'>　　商或有流移寓户或新近因飢荒各處逃來潛住</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l162' data-llen='3490:3513'>　　者俱不必逐離不時扵冊内陸續開報年終一併</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l163' data-llen='3513:3536'>　　通算計要見尚在者㡬人已去者幾人新來者㡬</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l164' data-llen='3536:3559'>　　人但有面目生疎之人蹤跡可疑之事即便阻逐</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l165' data-llen='3559:3578'>　　故縱者事發約正保長人等一體有罪</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l166' data-llen='3578:3601'>　七曰恤困窮　保内如有殘廢病弱及貧薄無倚之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l167' data-llen='3601:3624'>　　人各責令親黨收養毋令失所如無親黨許編入</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l168' data-llen='3624:3647'>　　有財力之家壯丁内夾帶如一牌夫下有四丁強</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l169' data-llen='3647:3674'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0090', 'WYG', '006-10a' );" name="006-10a" class="pb">[006-10a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l170' data-llen='3674:3697'>　　壯者即夾帶殘弱一人於内凡守望備警仍量存</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l171' data-llen='3697:3708'>　　之不得需索帮補</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l172' data-llen='3708:3731'>　八曰防行旅　保内常禁宵行夜逰每一更三點禁</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l173' data-llen='3731:3754'>　　人行各於閭巷之間設為鹿角之類以斷行路仍</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l174' data-llen='3754:3777'>　　擊木柝以傳更及五更三點放人行即除去之其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l175' data-llen='3777:3800'>　　有行旅止宿者除執節公使及官使或公差有明</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l176' data-llen='3800:3823'>　　文者不察外如國有大故遙聞寇戎大喪恐有姦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l177' data-llen='3823:3846'>　　非則令合守閭巷如有過客異常雖單騎孤囊或</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l178' data-llen='3846:3873'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0090', 'WYG', '006-10b' );" name="006-10b" class="pb">[006-10b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l179' data-llen='3873:3896'>　　為僧道服飾變詐多端務使人不疑者決是盜賊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l180' data-llen='3896:3919'>　　量行擒捕送官懲治若無干碍之人偶來宿歇則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l181' data-llen='3919:3935'>　　道之出境或染疾病共養視之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l182' data-llen='3935:3958'>　凡保長統領牌甲其法甚約其治甚廣盖軍民之均</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l183' data-llen='3958:3981'>　　編則紀綱之操縱可舉村社之詳明則公事之勾</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l184' data-llen='3981:4004'>　　攝可據丁力之多寡則糧差之分派可執生理之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l185' data-llen='4004:4027'>　　虛實則行止之善否可稽牛馬之有無則賑濟之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l186' data-llen='4027:4050'>　　等第可别往来之稽驗則訟獄之曲直可憑正長</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l187' data-llen='4050:4077'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0090', 'WYG', '006-11a' );" name="006-11a" class="pb">[006-11a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l188' data-llen='4077:4100'>　　之得失則里老之公私可分盜賊之有無則鄉村</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l189' data-llen='4100:4123'>　　之臧否可識彼此之聫絡則逃移之實數可查因</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l190' data-llen='4123:4146'>　　是而修之裒其多而益其寡則徭役可均因是而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l191' data-llen='4146:4169'>　　修之連其伍而制其什則外侮可禦因是而修之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l192' data-llen='4169:4192'>　　警其薄而勸其厚則風俗可淳因是而修之導以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l193' data-llen='4192:4215'>　　徳而訓以學則禮樂可興小而一縣大而一州不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l194' data-llen='4215:4238'>　　必更立法制固已如指諸掌矣凡有司宜與四隅</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l195' data-llen='4238:4261'>　　大館遙領鄉約著實舉行潤色而修舉之毋徒為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l196' data-llen='4261:4288'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0090', 'WYG', '006-11b' );" name="006-11b" class="pb">[006-11b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l197' data-llen='4288:4306'>　　紙上虛言則治化可以不勞而致矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l198' data-llen='4306:4329'>　凡有寇變各保彼此相援有司亦出兵助之或張威</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l199' data-llen='4329:4352'>　　以挫其鋒或設伏以要其歸路務使以逸待勞不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l200' data-llen='4352:4369'>　　為所詐寇平之日有司必加重賞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l201' data-llen='4369:4392'>　凡立十家甲牌專為止息盜賊若使毎甲各自糾察</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l202' data-llen='4392:4415'>　　甲内之人不得容留盜賊上甲如此下甲復如此</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l203' data-llen='4415:4438'>　　城郭鄉村無不如此以至此縣如此彼縣如此逺</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l204' data-llen='4438:4461'>　　近州縣無不如此則盜賊亦何自而生夫以一甲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l205' data-llen='4461:4488'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0090', 'WYG', '006-12a' );" name="006-12a" class="pb">[006-12a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l206' data-llen='4488:4511'>　　之人而各自糾察十家之内為力甚易使一甲而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l207' data-llen='4511:4534'>　　容一賊十甲即容十賊百甲即容百賊千甲即容</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l208' data-llen='4534:4557'>　　千賊矣衆賊至扵千百雖起一縣之兵而剿除之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l209' data-llen='4557:4580'>　　為力固己甚難今有司往往平日不嚴十家之法</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l210' data-llen='4580:4603'>　　及至盜賊充斥却乃興師動衆欲扵某處屯兵某</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l211' data-llen='4603:4626'>　　處截捕不治其本而治其末不為其易而為其難</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l212' data-llen='4626:4649'>　　皆由平日怠忽因循未嘗思念及此也自今務令</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l213' data-llen='4649:4672'>　　各甲各自糾察甲内有平日習為盜賊者除送官</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l214' data-llen='4672:4699'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0090', 'WYG', '006-12b' );" name="006-12b" class="pb">[006-12b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l215' data-llen='4699:4722'>　　外其或遇惡未稔尚可教戒者照依牌諭報名在</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l216' data-llen='4722:4745'>　　官令其改化自新時加點名省諭甲總輪流沿門</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l217' data-llen='4745:4766'>　　覺察如此則奸偽無所容而盜賊自可息矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l218' data-llen='4766:4789'>　凡保甲所以不行者其弊端有三一曰壯丁上牌人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l219' data-llen='4789:4812'>　　懼僉名輾轉為軍甲可乙否不肯編造二曰保長</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l220' data-llen='4812:4835'>　　約正人之善静無能者不喜承當或有喜功生事</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l221' data-llen='4835:4858'>　　借此營私身有過惡借此掩覆則樂為之人心不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l222' data-llen='4858:4881'>　　服建立不成三曰盜賊之徒犯約之過有告報在</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l223' data-llen='4881:4908'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0090', 'WYG', '006-13a' );" name="006-13a" class="pb">[006-13a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l224' data-llen='4908:4931'>　　官他日報讐反陷不測若有司於編造之時明出</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l225' data-llen='4931:4954'>　　告示破其疑惑有告報窩盜賭博非為等事給與</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l226' data-llen='4954:4977'>　　執照則人必樂扵行矣若保甲巡防戒諭著有成</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l227' data-llen='4977:4995'>　　効者縣官備禮親造其廬重加奬勵</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l228' data-llen='4995:5018'>　　　右件出陽明王氏保甲條約參以大學衍義補</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l229' data-llen='5018:5041'>　　　及保甲條件等書有司遙加領轄務以明道為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l230' data-llen='5041:5064'>　　　法王安石為戒毋得指此科罰點閘以致擾民</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l231' data-llen='5064:5067'>　</span><br/>
